<p itemprop="description">Innovation and emerging technology involves identifying, evaluating, and implementing new technologies and innovative approaches to improve government services and digital transformation.</p>

<div class="proficiency-levels">
    <h2>Proficiency Levels</h2>

    <ol class="skill-levels">
        <li>
            <h3>Awareness</h3>
            <p>You can understand the importance of innovation in government and recognise emerging technology trends and their potential applications.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Working</h3>
            <p>You can research emerging technologies, assess their relevance to government needs, and contribute to innovation initiatives and pilot projects.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Practitioner</h3>
            <p>You can lead innovation projects, evaluate emerging technologies for adoption, and develop strategies for implementing innovative solutions in government contexts.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Expert</h3>
            <p>You can drive enterprise innovation strategy, establish innovation frameworks and culture, and influence government technology policy and adoption of emerging technologies.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
</div>

